Dr. Chen's Background






Bio


John S. Chen, DDS is a practicing Pediatric Dentist in Agoura Hills, CA. Dr. Chen accepts multiple insurance plans including Aetna, Guardian Dental and Humana Dental. Dr. Chen also practices at Ronald Reagan UCLA Medical Center in Los Angeles, CA. 





